Lee Da Won!

4
00:00:58,866 --> 00:01:00,793
- Lee Da Won.
- Da Won!

5
00:01:00,793 --> 00:01:03,187
Lee Da Won's cell phone signal was last detected

6
00:01:03,188 --> 00:01:05,814
from the repeater in Seongnae Stream, Jeonmuk Valley.

7
00:01:05,815 --> 00:01:07,191
She's new but still a ranger.

8
00:01:07,192 --> 00:01:08,842
