9
00:01:08,842 --> 00:01:12,388
There's a dead tree southeast of Hurricane Lily Habitat in Jeonmuk Valley.

10
00:01:12,388 --> 00:01:14,114
We must check under that tree.

11
00:01:14,115 --> 00:01:15,699
That signal only you and Hyun Jo know?

12
00:01:15,700 --> 00:01:16,600
What's that?

13
00:01:16,600 --> 00:01:17,893
It's near the pebbly road at Haebawi Rock.

14
00:01:17,893 --> 00:01:19,937
How did it go? Did you find her?

15
00:01:19,937 --> 00:01:21,589
We found a pink-colored cell phone.

16
00:01:21,589 --> 00:01:22,940
It's covered in blood.

17
00:01:22,940 --> 00:01:24,650
But... what about Captain Jo Dae Jin?

18
00:01:24,650 --> 00:01:26,694
So this was recorded on Da Won's phone?

19
00:01:26,694 --> 00:01:27,903
Then, let's go down together.

20
00:01:27,903 --> 00:01:30,030
No. I'll go by myself.

21
00:01:30,030 --> 00:01:32,299
Haedong Two! Found the missing at the Amleung Ridge!

22
00:01:32,299 --> 00:01:34,034
How's Da Won? Is she all right?

23
00:01:34,034 --> 00:01:36,604
The missing... has no pulse and is not breathing.

24
00:01:36,604 --> 00:01:37,688
Presumed dead.

25
00:01:37,688 --> 00:01:39,331
We have a couple of things to ask you.

26
00:01:39,331 --> 00:01:42,418
The deceased... was holding this in her hand.

27
00:01:42,418 --> 00:01:44,478
Did you do that to Da Won?

28
00:01:44,479 --> 00:01:45,504
Why did you do it?

29
00:01:45,504 --> 00:01:46,672
And Hyun Jo, too?

30
00:01:46,672 --> 00:01:48,966
Did you do that to Hyun Jo?

31
00:01:48,966 --> 00:01:51,468
Why did you do that? Why?

32
00:01:51,468 --> 00:01:54,013
Tell Seo Yi Kang at Haedong Ranger Station

33
00:01:54,013 --> 00:01:56,374
that I didn't leave the mark this time.

34
00:01:56,374 --> 00:01:59,935
He said he didn't leave the mark this time?

35
00:01:59,935 --> 00:02:02,171
When you and Hyun Jo had that accident,

36
00:02:02,171 --> 00:02:04,089
why did you go to Black Bridge Valley?

37
00:02:04,089 --> 00:02:06,508
What happened to you and Hyun Jo?

38
00:02:06,508 --> 00:02:08,819
What were you doing with Da Won?

39
00:02:08,819 --> 00:02:10,738
Why do you suspect the captain?

40
00:02:10,738 --> 00:02:12,965
Why did you return to the mountain?

41
00:02:12,966 --> 00:02:14,867
I can't understand any of it.

42
00:02:14,867 --> 00:02:16,560
Maybe you shouldn't have come back.

43
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:20,481
When do you think... we can quit this work?

44
00:02:20,481 --> 00:02:23,183
It's not something you can quit when you want to.

45
00:02:23,184 --> 00:02:24,945
It involves saving people's lives.

46
00:02:24,945 --> 00:02:27,446
Saving people's lives is our job.

47
00:02:27,446 --> 00:02:31,489
But I'm seeing more dead people than live ones.

48
00:02:31,489 --> 00:02:32,660
Do you remember him?
[Chairperson Yang Geun Tak]

49
00:02:32,660 --> 00:02:34,720
He's come back to the mountain.

50
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:37,139
The mountain spirit will be infuriated once again.

51
00:02:37,139 --> 00:02:39,308
The mountain spirit is not the only one up there.

52
00:02:39,308 --> 00:02:41,361
Grandma told me a long time ago,

53
00:02:41,361 --> 00:02:44,630
that the evil spirit comes before the mountain spirit.

54
00:02:44,630 --> 00:02:46,123
Black Bridge Valley Village.

55
00:02:46,124 --> 00:02:48,984
Have you forgotten all that's happened there?

56
00:02:48,984 --> 00:02:52,070
Never forget, especially the Black Bridge Valley area.

57
00:02:52,070 --> 00:02:54,089
Don't ever go there.

58
00:02:54,090 --> 00:02:56,617
Black Bridge Valley.

59
00:03:01,450 --> 00:03:04,550
[1991]

60
00:03:23,411 --> 00:03:26,170
Over there is Black Bridge Valley Village.

61
00:03:26,170 --> 00:03:28,798
Oh, I see.

62
00:03:28,798 --> 00:03:32,903
This place is a perfect location for cable cars.

63
00:03:32,903 --> 00:03:38,700
We'd appreciate some help from the national park to get consent from the villagers.

64
00:03:38,700 --> 00:03:43,031
It'll be good for the mountain and the residents.

65
00:03:46,459 --> 00:03:48,527
The national park regulations require that we stay neutral.

66
00:03:48,527 --> 00:03:51,480
Our job is to show the roads.

67
00:03:51,481 --> 00:03:55,417
Yeah, okay...

68
00:04:07,689 --> 00:04:09,590
How have you been?

69
00:04:11,342 --> 00:04:14,895
We brought you a guest.

70
00:04:14,895 --> 00:04:17,931
Please say hello. This is the mayor of Black Bridge Valley Village.

71
00:04:17,931 --> 00:04:19,725
Hello.

72
00:04:19,725 --> 00:04:23,988
I'm Yang Geun Tak, the president of the Jirisan Development Committee.

73
00:04:29,569 --> 00:04:31,570
My name is Kim Jae Gyeong.

74
00:04:31,570 --> 00:04:33,606
Ah, yes.

75
00:04:44,309 --> 00:04:46,311
- Leave!
- Jae Gyeong, stop!

76
00:04:46,311 --> 00:04:48,988
- Get out of here!
- Please stop!

77
00:04:51,608 --> 00:04:54,426
We have no intention of moving out. Leave.

78
00:04:54,426 --> 00:04:56,845
Mr. Kim.

79
00:04:56,845 --> 00:04:59,682
I told you we'll give you

80
00:04:59,682 --> 00:05:02,492
as much relocation compensation as possible.

81
00:05:02,492 --> 00:05:04,578
This uppity— Seriously.

82
00:05:04,578 --> 00:05:07,748
Do you think this is about greed for money?

83
00:05:07,748 --> 00:05:10,993
This place is our home and where we stem from.

84
00:05:11,961 --> 00:05:15,972
We have no further business. Please leave.

85
00:05:16,591 --> 00:05:18,384
You'll all...

86
00:05:23,723 --> 00:05:26,134
absolutely regret this.

87
00:06:53,830 --> 00:06:55,390
Oh, dear.

88
00:06:55,390 --> 00:06:57,366
What happened?

89
00:06:57,366 --> 00:06:59,930
Oh, my.

90
00:06:59,930 --> 00:07:01,720
Anyway,

91
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:05,721
- Can't even take a shower.
- Excuse me, passing through.

92
00:07:06,409 --> 00:07:08,368
What happened?

93
00:07:08,368 --> 00:07:09,920
Look in there.

94
00:07:15,251 --> 00:07:18,270
Who could have done such a thing?

95
00:07:18,271 --> 00:07:20,356
It's him! The cable car man.

96
00:07:21,215 --> 00:07:24,933
He messed with the well to kick us out from here!

97
00:07:24,933 --> 00:07:26,286
That's right. That's right.

98
00:07:26,286 --> 00:07:29,281
- It was him.
- Yes, it must be him.

99
00:07:29,282 --> 00:07:33,636
Has anyone seen him putting that in there?

100
00:07:34,287 --> 00:07:35,996
We've not seen him do it.

101
00:07:35,997 --> 00:07:38,440
We can't report him to the police when we're not even sure.

102
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:40,292
Are you saying we should do nothing?

103
00:07:40,293 --> 00:07:44,438
This might not be the end. He could do something else to us.

104
00:07:45,656 --> 00:07:47,741
Don't worry too much.

105
00:07:47,741 --> 00:07:51,411
We'll do more patrols.

106
00:07:51,411 --> 00:07:54,473
And think of ways to enhance village security.

107
00:07:56,751 --> 00:08:00,454
We'll protect you with all our might!

108
00:08:02,715 --> 00:08:04,642
Please do not worry.

109
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:10,807
[Jo Dae Jin]

110
00:08:10,807 --> 00:08:12,432
People started dying.

111
00:08:12,432 --> 00:08:15,102
Three people died from this small village.

112
00:08:15,102 --> 00:08:18,030
Can this be just a coincidence?

113
00:08:19,565 --> 00:08:23,519
Did you guys hear that just now?

114
00:08:34,889 --> 00:08:37,958
Is this the Black Bridge Valley Village?

115
00:08:37,958 --> 00:08:40,669
Yes, sir. It's supposed to be in the Deokseoryeong area.

116
00:08:40,669 --> 00:08:43,356
But it doesn't show on the map.

117
00:08:49,887 --> 00:08:51,805
Shouldn't we go look?

118
00:08:51,805 --> 00:08:53,849
Has there been any missing report?

119
00:08:53,849 --> 00:08:55,376
No.

120
00:08:57,937 --> 00:08:59,797
Then don't worry about it.

121
00:09:02,608 --> 00:09:05,527
We've had a lot of people asking for time off lately.

122
00:09:05,527 --> 00:09:07,212
Even if we are short-staffed, please plan thoroughly

123
00:09:07,213 --> 00:09:11,591
and resolve the mountain spirit ritual without an issue.

124
00:09:11,592 --> 00:09:13,552
But, Sir.

125
00:09:13,552 --> 00:09:15,245
That's enough.

126
00:09:15,245 --> 00:09:19,140
He could've staged this for more views.

127
00:09:19,141 --> 00:09:20,834
But it could be real.

128
00:09:20,834 --> 00:09:23,103
Looks like his cell phone was working well enough to post the video.

129
00:09:23,104 --> 00:09:25,589
If he were in real danger, he would've called for help.

130
00:09:25,589 --> 00:09:27,924
He dropped his phone and the video ended.

131
00:09:27,924 --> 00:09:30,870
Maybe the phone broke, so he couldn't call.

132
00:09:32,346 --> 00:09:34,990
You spent two hours carrying that jerk down.

133
00:09:34,991 --> 00:09:36,241
It will be exactly like that.

134
00:09:36,241 --> 00:09:40,304
You go up there for this, there's a 98% chance it's nothing.

135
00:09:41,706 --> 00:09:45,367
Something about it bothers you too, to take the 2% off.

