142
00:11:17,594 --> 00:11:21,280
Something's off with the satellite phone battery.

143
00:11:22,376 --> 00:11:27,520
Ah, that Jung Goo Yeong, I told him to check the devices carefully.

144
00:11:28,305 --> 00:11:30,948
I'll do it when we get back.

145
00:11:30,948 --> 00:11:33,568
Never mind that. Just take this.

146
00:11:33,568 --> 00:11:36,011
What's this?

147
00:11:36,011 --> 00:11:39,849
Ghosts are supposed to come from the north today.

148
00:11:39,849 --> 00:11:43,285
I was warned not to go near Black Bridge Valley today.

149
00:11:44,228 --> 00:11:46,313
I guess you don't actually hate me.

150
00:11:46,313 --> 00:11:48,816
Since you care about me like this.

151
00:11:51,150 --> 00:11:54,154
Are you trying to climb over me?

152
00:11:54,154 --> 00:11:57,416
I'm a ranger. Must be good at climbing in general.

153
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:59,752
Let's go.

154
00:12:01,887 --> 00:12:03,914
Hey!

155
00:12:03,914 --> 00:12:05,841
Wrong way.

156
00:12:26,100 --> 00:12:28,621
There's not a single soul here.

157
00:12:28,622 --> 00:12:30,649
Should we go back?

158
00:12:30,649 --> 00:12:33,903
- Wrestling will start soon.
- Wrestling, my butt.

159
00:12:33,903 --> 00:12:38,474
Keep searching carefully. You never know when accidents happen.

160
00:12:46,826 --> 00:12:49,809
- Oh? Hey, what's that?
- Woah!

161
00:12:49,810 --> 00:12:51,779
- Woah!
- Stop the car.

162
00:12:58,510 --> 00:13:01,304
Mister! Mister!

163
00:13:01,304 --> 00:13:03,123
Mister, are you okay?

164
00:13:03,123 --> 00:13:04,891
Call for 119, hurry.

165
00:13:04,891 --> 00:13:06,194
Mister!

166
00:13:06,194 --> 00:13:07,977
- Whoa!
- Go away!

167
00:13:07,977 --> 00:13:10,248
Get off me!

168
00:13:10,248 --> 00:13:13,269
Calm down. We're the police.

169
00:13:13,269 --> 00:13:16,529
Ghost... Ghost lights.

170
00:13:16,529 --> 00:13:19,097
I saw ghost lights.

171
00:13:19,097 --> 00:13:20,590
I saw ghost lights.

172
00:13:20,591 --> 00:13:22,076
Ghost lights!

173
00:13:22,076 --> 00:13:23,618
Ghost...

174
00:13:23,618 --> 00:13:25,829
Up there.

175
00:13:27,164 --> 00:13:29,450
Ghost lights.

176
00:13:33,998 --> 00:13:37,774
Oh... Okay, sir.

177
00:13:46,809 --> 00:13:48,344
Granny...

178
00:13:49,670 --> 00:13:51,229
Hey, what are you doing?

179
00:13:51,229 --> 00:13:53,156
Didn't you go to work today?

180
00:13:53,156 --> 00:13:56,985
- Neither did you?
- I only do it once in a while.

181
00:13:56,985 --> 00:13:59,237
How could you be off all the time?

182
00:13:59,237 --> 00:14:02,173
What do you mean all the time?

183
00:14:02,174 --> 00:14:04,118
Oh, hey.

184
00:14:04,118 --> 00:14:06,745
- Mr. Park.
- Hello.

185
00:14:06,745 --> 00:14:08,371
- Did you eat?
- Not yet.

186
00:14:08,371 --> 00:14:10,006
One second. I'll make it quick.

187
00:14:10,006 --> 00:14:12,240
Take your time.

188
00:14:12,240 --> 00:14:13,640
Breaking up is...

189
00:14:13,640 --> 00:14:15,587
What are you doing?

190
00:14:16,355 --> 00:14:18,156
Don't.

191
00:14:19,191 --> 00:14:21,050
What are you guys up to?

192
00:14:22,090 --> 00:14:24,204
A day off?

193
00:14:25,890 --> 00:14:27,457
- Yes, it is!
- What's wrong with that?

194
00:14:27,457 --> 00:14:29,328
- Don't you get days off?
- I take every day off.

195
00:14:29,328 --> 00:14:32,020
He takes days off all the time but me, only rarely.

196
00:14:32,020 --> 00:14:35,350
Why are you all coming for me? Take as much as you want. Okay, okay.

197
00:14:35,350 --> 00:14:36,635
You guys.

198
00:14:36,635 --> 00:14:39,444
Anyway, have you watched that video yesterday?

199
00:14:39,444 --> 00:14:41,863
The guy who posted that Black Bridge Valley video?

200
00:14:41,863 --> 00:14:47,094
We found him by the road and took him to the hospital earlier, but he was totally out of his mind.

201
00:14:47,786 --> 00:14:50,830
Didn't Yi Kang and Hyun Jo go there earlier?

202
00:14:50,830 --> 00:14:52,665
Yes... Black Bridge Village in Deokseoryeong.

203
00:14:52,665 --> 00:14:54,292
What are you saying?

204
00:14:54,292 --> 00:14:55,835
Yi Kang went to where?

205
00:14:55,835 --> 00:14:57,670
To Black Bridge Valley Village?

206
00:14:57,670 --> 00:14:59,380
Yes.

207
00:14:59,380 --> 00:15:00,632
What?

208
00:15:00,632 --> 00:15:03,760
Black Bridge Valley Village in the north.

209
00:15:03,760 --> 00:15:05,762
She can't go north today.

210
00:15:05,762 --> 00:15:09,949
It's the day ghosts come from the north.

211
00:15:13,055 --> 00:15:16,689
Whoa. Now, this is something.

212
00:15:16,689 --> 00:15:18,525
When did the village get demolished?

213
00:15:18,525 --> 00:15:20,860
I heard in 1991.

214
00:15:20,860 --> 00:15:24,072
- Is this your first time here, too?
- I never had a reason to come.

215
00:15:24,072 --> 00:15:28,560
There's nothing to see here, plus it's dangerous, so people rarely come here.

216
00:15:46,760 --> 00:15:48,722
Hello?

217
00:15:54,995 --> 00:15:56,997
Anyone there?

218
00:15:56,997 --> 00:15:59,375
We're from the national park.

219
00:16:01,020 --> 00:16:02,926
Anyone?

220
00:16:22,530 --> 00:16:23,756
See?

221
00:16:23,756 --> 00:16:27,202
I said there's a 98% chance it's nothing.

222
00:16:27,202 --> 00:16:29,387
If he got stranded, it must be around here.

223
00:16:29,387 --> 00:16:33,725
Check the bushes, he probably went into it.

224
00:16:35,436 --> 00:16:37,387
Let's check that side.

225
00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:44,260
[Kim Jae Gyeong]

226
00:17:15,350 --> 00:17:17,600
Hello?

227
00:17:17,600 --> 00:17:19,655
Anyone there?

228
00:17:21,940 --> 00:17:24,568
We're from the national park.

229
00:17:24,568 --> 00:17:26,503
Nobody?

230
00:17:42,227 --> 00:17:43,753
What's wrong?

231
00:17:44,755 --> 00:17:46,123
Huh?

232
00:17:48,350 --> 00:17:49,809
What is this?

233
00:17:49,809 --> 00:17:52,720
We're back to where we started.

234
00:17:52,720 --> 00:17:55,598
I think we're lost.

235
00:17:55,598 --> 00:17:57,517
Turn your GPS on.

236
00:17:58,420 --> 00:18:00,280
[Error]

